- {{ label }}: {{ description }}
{% endfor %}

### Output Format
Respond with a single JSON object and nothing else:

  {"order": ["label-1", "label-2", ...]}

List every label exactly once, copied verbatim from the list above, in
the order they should be established. Do not wrap the JSON in code
fences and do not add any explanation before or after it.
